text: Novyye Sulli () is a rural locality (a selo) in Starosullinsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 290 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km from Yermekeyevo, 3 km from Staryye Sulli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Novyye Sulli
